OL,6,FThe lines between gaming and gambling
OL,7,Fare becoming increasingly blurred,
OL,8,Fwith features such as loot boxes, pack
OL,9,Fopenings and gaming streaks.
OL,11,FWhile these activities don't
OL,12,Ftechnically fall under the UK's legal
OL,13,Fdefinition of gambling, their
OL,14,Faddictive nature and financial
OL,15,Fimplications suggest otherwise.
OL,17,FMany argue that the addictive nature
OL,18,Fof these activities is alarmingly
OL,19,Fsimilar to gambling.
