OL,6,FData given to us exclusively by
OL,7,FGamCare, suggests the number of calls
OL,8,Fto gambling helplines related to
OL,9,Fgaming has doubled in the past year,
OL,10,Freaching an all-time high.
OL,12,FIn the financial year 2023-24, the
OL,13,FNational Gambling Helpline saw 129
OL,14,Findividual callers disclose video
OL,15,Fgames as one of their gambling-related
OL,16,Factivities, the highest of any year in
OL,17,Frecord and over double the previous
OL,18,Fyear.
