OL,6,FAdditionally, in the calendar years
OL,7,F2022 and 2023, 15% of the young people
OL,8,Freferred to GamCare's Young People
OL,9,FService were referred in for gaming-
OL,10,Frelated harm.
OL,12,FYoung people, especially under-18s,
OL,13,Ffind online gambling and gambling-like
OL,14,Factivities disturbingly accessible.
OL,15,FPopular platforms like EA FC, Roblox,
OL,16,Fand Fortnite often feature these
OL,17,Fmechanisms, including purchasing loot
OL,18,Fboxes or receiving rewards for
OL,19,Fmaintaining streaks.
OL,21,FWhat is a 'Gambling-Like' Activity?
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G3/10
