OL,6,F, the term "gambling-like activity"
OL,7,Fcan be confusing, especially for
OL,8,Fyounger people who may not recognise
OL,9,Ftheir behaviour as gambling.
OL,11,FCommon forms include loot boxes
OL,12,Fvirtual items that can be bought or
OL,13,Fearned, containing random rewards.
OL,14,FStreak rewards, incentives for
OL,15,Fconsecutive daily logins or activities
OL,16,Fthat mimic gambling reward systems.
