OL,6,FMany young people report engaging in
OL,7,Fthese activities to relieve boredom or
OL,8,Ffor enjoyment, often not recognising
OL,9,Fthem as gambling. They also believe
OL,10,Fthat if little or no money is
OL,11,Finvolved, or if there is an element of
OL,12,Fskill, it doesn't count as gambling.
OL,14,FCharities are calling for new
OL,15,Fvocabulary and clearer definitions to
OL,16,Faddress these grey areas.
