OL,6,FEA and Roblox both declined to comment
OL,7,Fon the report, however, Epic Games
OL,8,Fsaid: "This report misrepresents how
OL,9,FFortnite operates.
OL,11,F"We have never had gambling in
OL,12,FFortnite and there are no paid random
OL,13,Fitem loot boxes. Fortnite is free to
OL,14,Fdownload, there are no pay-to-win
OL,15,Fmechanics and players don't need to
OL,16,Fmake purchases to get access to
OL,17,Fgameplay updates."
